<p><span><span style="color: #ff6600;">EN</span>:</span></p>
<ol>
<li>Store owner will receive notification email after receiving new product review.&nbsp;</li>
<li>If there are pending reviews - standart notification toolbar is shown in admin.&nbsp;</li>
<li>There is a function, that makes it difficult for auto bots/spammers to submit reviews.</li>
</ol>
<p>Thanks for idea with toolbar to module&nbsp;&nbsp; http://www.magentocommerce.com/magento-connect/clockworkgeek/extension/3853/clockworkgeek_reviewsnotification</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Installation</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>* Disable Compiler, if it is enabled (System -&gt; Tools -&gt; Compilation)</li>
<li>* Disable cache, if it is enabled (System -&gt; Cache Management)</li>
<li>* Install the extension</li>
<li>* Log off admin panel (Log Out)</li>
<li>* Log into admin panel (enter your login and password)</li>
<li>* Set Advanced Compare parameters (System -&gt; Configuration -&gt; Catalog -&gt; Product Reviews)</li>
<li>* Run compilation process and enable cache if needed</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Features</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>* Open source code (no encryption and obfuscation)</li>
<li>* Code follows Magento development standards</li>
<li>* Extension is available on 2 languages (ru_RU, en_US) and you can easy add your own</li>
<li>* All extension settings are available on admin panel</li>
<li>** Enable/Disable email notification</li>
<li>** Enable/Disable toolbar notification&nbsp;</li>
<li>** Notification email template can be changed</li>
<li>** Email notification to multiple recipients</li>
<li>** Enable/Disable Anti spam function</li>
<li>* Theme modification is not required if you have original element names on your review form.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
